      · repeat first | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by positivity ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | rw [ Real.sqrt_mul <| by unreachable! ] | ring;
